imdb.plot outline: Rude Girl: The antics of a silly cute girl as she messes with the people that knock on her front door. The Job: The silly weird life of an overworked and underpaid private eye and the people who call his office. His funny sarcastic secretary, Boomqueesha is busy at work not doing her work and resents Scott for asking her to.
imdb.title: What Up/Rude Girl
plot: The antics of a funny, cute girl as she (unknowingly to her parents) gives people a hard time that knock on her door...::Scott Alan Berk, Madison Rose
